{"tid":731570,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"J洛獨憔悴 軒達臣安慰","createTime":"2018-07-06T09:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T09:58:55.000Z","uid":7715,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5cfc5e575c02cab38132f81ff91c0835e84b37e5","tid":731570,"uid":7715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/06/173829_a8b0546d562374f0600a7e87950bc9a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F06%2F173829_a8b0546d562374f0600a7e87950bc9a0.jpg&h=66127170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=tIRv%2FMGLmht8M4%2Fqae7CxwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=bf5a9a26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】英格蘭中場佐敦軒達臣賽後盡顯風度，安慰受傷缺陣的哥倫比亞中場占士洛迪古斯。<br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞球星占士洛迪古斯因傷無緣16強，賽後見證球隊互射12碼落敗，不禁在後備席流下英雄淚，在互射12碼時宴客的佐敦軒達臣（Jordan Hendenson）顯然明白人家失望心情，見狀上前安慰一番，盡顯勝利者的風度。<br />\n<br />\n26歲的占士洛迪古斯心情猶如過山車，賽前一直努力希望能趕及披甲，結果卻連後備席也無緣就坐。全場看到球隊都落後1球，不禁心焦如焚；當看到耶利文拿完場前頂入追平，他從座位上站起慶祝。及至互射12碼決勝時，他落場鼓勵隊友努力，可惜最後射12碼以3:4落敗。<br />\n<br />\n占士洛迪古斯是上屆決賽周神射手，帶領球隊殺入8強僅負巴西。可惜，這位上季效力拜仁慕尼黑的球星近年收到傷病困擾，來到決賽周也難逃一劫，僅提供2個助攻，最終因傷錯過16強。"},{"pid":"94fea6931e7f68d3dbc0475589932b1e5326b2bc","tid":731570,"uid":9708,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:39:56.000Z","msg":"寂寞憔悴 條係賓周你個咀"},{"pid":"a8135f4e6d5071c8d441be9a49425a9c2eca54eb","tid":731570,"uid":47268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:40:08.000Z","msg":"撚狗咁撚"},{"pid":"3362f3d88d422ed42eca65ba389671251f3179cb","tid":731570,"uid":7715,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a8135f4e6d5071c8d441be9a49425a9c2eca54eb","tid":731570,"uid":47268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:40:08.000Z","msg":"撚狗咁撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:43:00.000Z","msg":"上前安慰一番，盡顯勝利者的風度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5b1d2c47bc79445e7aee2ec7f9fff5b7085e41","tid":731570,"uid":106675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:44:47.000Z","msg":": 幫到你盡"},{"pid":"66873dbcbf37cd9f16532f2a06758f5f9c28a165","tid":731570,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:47:38.000Z","msg":"軒隊長真係一個好完美既男人"},{"pid":"f76941eeb70dc23750e68162cf0e9e2b6181b196","tid":731570,"uid":17628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:53:14.000Z","msg":"鶯咕咕"},{"pid":"9d9c714013bf1b30b5105b25fc689a0744212724","tid":731570,"uid":13097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:57:21.000Z","msg":"慰安婦"},{"pid":"75b7c44904b65cfdaa0e2d61c2a7fa0f89d8f633","tid":731570,"uid":153795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:58:14.000Z","msg":"岩岩輸完r聯 梗係明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008fe32371be852bf7facab33c14c4553287569b","tid":731570,"uid":28540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:58:55.000Z","msg":"差d輸你呢條撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}